Linearly normalize numbers in column 'banana' to be in range [0,1].
perltab --test -pe 'beminmax $min, $max, F(banana)'  -e2 'donum  sub{ $_= ($_-$min) / ($max-$min) },  F(banana)'  t/regression/input/fruit.tsv
